26:02.961 --> 26:06.832 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
staff to American officials both
inside and outside Afghanistan,

26:06.865 --> 26:12.805 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
the hospital was hammered by the
American AC-130 gunship. The

26:12.838 --> 26:15.507 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
attack followed days of heavy
fighting in Kunduz as Afghan and

26:15.541 --> 26:19.211 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
American forces fought to retake
the city from the Taliban.

26:19.244 --> 26:21.980 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Today, Campbell said the plane's
crew had been given faulty

26:22.014 --> 26:25.684 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
