suspected Taliban base. GEN.

26:25.717 --> 26:28.454 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
JOHN CAMPBELL: That U.S. strike
upon the MSF trauma center in

26:28.487 --> 26:33.258 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Kunduz city, Afghanistan, was
the direct result of human error

26:33.292 --> 26:36.895 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
