26:47.005 --> 26:50.042 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
SREENIVASAN: MSF has maintained
no armed fighters were in the

26:50.075 --> 26:53.011 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
area near the hospital when the
strike occurred. The group

26:53.045 --> 26:56.515 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
