27:23.342 --> 27:26.545 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
GORDON LUBOLD, The Wall Street
Journal: Right. So, what we

27:26.578 --> 27:29.781 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
learned from this report that
was released today at the

27:29.815 --> 27:33.018 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
