October 3 strike that

27:49.535 --> 27:54.172 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
contributed to just the wrong
targeting of the -- targeting of

27:54.206 --> 27:58.644 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
the wrong building in Kunduz
that night And it ended up being

27:58.677 --> 28:01.980 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
the hospital, not the building
several hundred meters away that

28:02.014 --> 28:04.616 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
