33:40.385 --> 33:43.755 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
telling space and time how to
curve and the curving of space

33:43.788 --> 33:47.459 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
and time telling bodies how to
move, and then the math goes

33:47.492 --> 33:50.528 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
with it. And it was just a
hugely -- it wasn't like a

33:50.562 --> 33:53.531 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
little improvement over Newton's
universe. It was just a whole

33:53.565 --> 33:55.533 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
