34:01.940 --> 34:05.844 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
relative depending on your state
of motion. Then 10 years ago,

34:05.877 --> 34:08.780 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
exactly 100 years ago this week,
he comes up with the

34:08.813 --> 34:13.618 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
generalization of the theory
that says acceleration, gravity,

34:13.652 --> 34:17.355 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
time, space, they're all
related, and these equations

34:17.389 --> 34:21.026 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
show how. GWEN IFILL: And the
