theories disproved or debunked,

38:07.785 --> 38:12.657 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
and then you wait a month or
two, and there has been nothing

38:12.690 --> 38:14.826 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
that has cut out the
underpinnings of general

38:14.859 --> 38:17.428 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
relativity, of all of
relativity. And even the ones

38:17.462 --> 38:20.532 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
